(20011, 'Goldfenac mr 75mg 20 tabs.', 'جولدفيناك ام ار 75 مجم 20 قرص', '', '24', 'Diclofenac sodium', 'Hochster pharmaceutical indusries > novell pharma', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Nsaid.acetic acid derivatives', '75mg', 'Diclofenac is indicated for use in the treatment of pain and inflammation from varying sources including inflammatory conditions such as osteoarthritis, rheumatoid arthritis, and ankylosing spondylitis, as well as injury-related inflammation due to surgery and physical trauma. It is often used in combination with [misoprostol] as a gastro-protective agent in patients with high risk of developing NSAID-induced ulcers.', '', '', 1014, '2022-07-12', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
(29295, 'Vigadol 100mg 4 f.c.tab', 'فيجادول 100مجم 4 قرص', '', '14', 'Sildenafil', 'El nasr', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Tonic for men', '100mg', 'Sildenafil is a phosphodiesterase-5 (PDE5) inhibitor that is predominantly employed for two primary indications:
